post_text:
Horizon Science Academy-Denison is a K-8, stem-focused school, recently awarded the Ohio Momentum Award, the Federal Community School of Quality Award, and we have been recognized as a School of Excellence by the Ohio Coalition for Quality Charter Schools.

Students in our school are taught with a college-preparatory focus. This includes college and career track classes, like robotics and web design.

We offer art, foreign languages, PE, character education, and computer classes.
We would love to share more information about our building and its campus. Enroll today at horizondenison.org or call for more information 216.739.9911
